 galaxies.\nFinally, a comparison between MIC and Spearman correlation coefficient shows\nthat the former is a more reliable indicator when halo properties are weakly\ncorrelated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Aug 2013 22:47:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Jan 2014 02:48:07 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 11 Mar 2014 14:35:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-03-12"}
